comments.text:
CSS animations should be stoppable like animated images, because they might be distracting.

When you press esc, BrowserStop() does this:
1964     const stopFlags = nsIWebNavigation.STOP_ALL;
1965     getWebNavigation().stop(stopFlags);
http://mxr.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/source/browser/base/content/browser.js#1961

